            <title>[LU-16594] Linux 6.2 client support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16594</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.1-13825-g3c202d14a9d7&lt;br/&gt;
  prandom: remove prandom_u32_max()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use get_random_u32_below() and provide a replacement&lt;br/&gt;
when get_random_u32_below is not available.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.1-rc1-2-g138060ba92b3&lt;br/&gt;
  fs: pass dentry to set acl method&lt;br/&gt;
Linux commit v6.1-rc1-4-g7420332a6ff4&lt;br/&gt;
  fs: add new get acl method&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;get_acl() and set_acl() have new signatures&lt;/p&gt;</description>
